WEBVTT

01:37.910 --> 01:40.990
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.070 --> 01:43.970
[Episode 8]

01:46.200 --> 01:48.600
I just want to add you on WeChat

01:48.950 --> 01:50.640
and ask you

01:50.640 --> 01:51.580
some professional questions.

01:51.580 --> 01:52.150
Sure.

01:52.310 --> 01:54.240
Give me the dry cleaning fee first.

01:54.310 --> 01:55.310
My custom-made suit

01:55.310 --> 01:56.870
costs 3,280 yuan to wash.

01:57.120 --> 01:58.450
Just give me 3,000 yuan.

01:59.280 --> 02:02.200
Mr. Ji, you can't blame me for all this.

02:02.200 --> 02:03.280
It was an accident.

02:03.280 --> 02:06.000
And look how crowded

02:06.000 --> 02:07.120
it is here.

02:10.669 --> 02:12.230
It's her.

02:13.000 --> 02:14.240
She pushed me just now,

02:14.240 --> 02:16.040
and that's why I bumped into you.

02:16.710 --> 02:18.840
How could I have bumped into you
from so far away?

02:18.840 --> 02:20.560
Didn't you just nudge me with your elbow

02:20.560 --> 02:21.630
so I couldn't stand firmly

02:21.630 --> 02:23.190
and bump into Mr. Ji?

02:28.860 --> 02:30.020
I remember now.

02:32.829 --> 02:36.210
You are the one
who asked me for wine just now,

02:36.240 --> 02:38.680
but found that I only had champagne
on my tray,

02:38.680 --> 02:40.280
not the red wine you wanted,

02:40.360 --> 02:42.020
so you turned around and left.

02:45.310 --> 02:46.280
It's all my fault.

02:46.280 --> 02:47.470
I only had champagne on my tray

02:47.470 --> 02:48.750
and not the red wine you wanted.

02:48.750 --> 02:51.400
It caused you to run to the dining table
so far away to get wine.

02:51.400 --> 02:53.770
so you accidentally bumped into Mr. Ji.

02:53.910 --> 02:55.490
It is indeed my poor service.

02:55.490 --> 02:56.280
I'm sorry.

02:56.390 --> 02:57.310
Nonsense!

02:58.400 --> 03:00.190
Xu Miyu, do you believe

03:00.190 --> 03:00.910
I'll file a complaint against you?

03:00.910 --> 03:01.840
Miss,

03:02.120 --> 03:03.190
may I ask—

03:03.470 --> 03:04.470
how exactly is she

03:04.470 --> 03:05.960
supposed to help you

03:05.990 --> 03:07.650
spill wine on this gentleman?

03:17.820 --> 03:18.579
Like this?

03:22.280 --> 03:23.030
What happened?

03:23.030 --> 03:24.910
Mr. Duan, they poured wine on me.

03:24.910 --> 03:26.940
This is unbelievably rude.

03:28.720 --> 03:30.050
You are not off work yet?

03:33.910 --> 03:34.910
Who did this?

03:35.240 --> 03:36.120
I didn't mean it!

03:36.120 --> 03:37.280
It's her. She pushed me.

03:37.280 --> 03:38.480
She did it on purpose.

03:39.190 --> 03:39.840
Miss,

03:40.120 --> 03:42.560
please speak logically, okay?

03:42.579 --> 03:44.579
What does she gain by setting you up?

03:44.840 --> 03:45.680
Are you going to marry her,

03:45.680 --> 03:47.280
or support her or something?

03:49.030 --> 03:49.930
Do I know you?

03:51.520 --> 03:53.160
I came with Vivian.

03:54.680 --> 03:55.560
Who is Vivian?

03:57.100 --> 03:58.000
Step forward!

04:00.310 --> 04:02.360
Sorry, there's no Vivian here.

04:03.210 --> 04:04.800
I need to see your invitation.

04:04.800 --> 04:06.080
Did you sneak in?

04:06.120 --> 04:06.730
No.

04:07.000 --> 04:08.130
I'll find it for you.

04:12.120 --> 04:13.240
Where is it?

04:18.390 --> 04:19.390
Seriously,

04:19.390 --> 04:20.240
can you stop letting people like this

04:20.240 --> 04:21.480
come in and ruin my event?

04:21.480 --> 04:22.270
Sorry, Mr. Duan.

04:22.270 --> 04:23.530
It won't happen again.

04:23.720 --> 04:25.270
It's fine, keep playing.

04:26.060 --> 04:26.840
It's fine.

04:27.000 --> 04:27.680
Go ahead.

04:27.870 --> 04:28.430
Come on.

04:28.510 --> 04:29.520
Let's continue.

04:30.120 --> 04:30.850
I'm sorry.

04:30.880 --> 04:31.800
Every time there's a party,

04:31.800 --> 04:33.800
there are always people
like this sneaking in.

04:33.800 --> 04:35.240
Take off your suit

04:35.240 --> 04:37.270
and I'll ask the hotel
to handle it for you.

04:37.270 --> 04:37.870
Forget it.

04:37.980 --> 04:39.610
Your laundry room
probably can't handle it.

04:39.610 --> 04:40.950
I'll figure it out myself.

04:40.950 --> 04:41.770
Mr. Ji,

04:42.120 --> 04:43.680
please let me take the suit.

04:44.390 --> 04:46.430
I know a dry cleaner on South Maoming Road

04:46.430 --> 04:48.000
that specializes in high-end suits.

04:48.000 --> 04:48.950
They do a great job.

04:48.950 --> 04:50.270
I'll take it there right now.

04:50.270 --> 04:51.330
Not too dumb.

04:51.720 --> 04:52.430
Go quickly.

04:52.800 --> 04:53.600
Have HSKP Department

04:53.600 --> 04:54.560
cover the money for now—

04:54.560 --> 04:55.890
charge it to my account.

04:56.830 --> 04:58.430
Then please hold this for me.

04:58.560 --> 04:59.159
Thank you.

05:09.870 --> 05:11.830
The HSKP Department has good taste.

05:11.830 --> 05:12.900
She's quite smart.

05:13.360 --> 05:14.160
And she's got

05:15.010 --> 05:16.010
her own charm too.

05:16.800 --> 05:18.600
Is she from the executive floor?

05:22.870 --> 05:24.290
What about that female chef?

05:24.290 --> 05:25.550
Did she run away again?

05:27.950 --> 05:28.390
Miyu.

05:31.240 --> 05:32.630
Why are you here?

05:32.800 --> 05:34.610
What's going on with you?

05:34.830 --> 05:36.240
You didn't pass the internal referral
last time.

05:36.240 --> 05:38.000
Didn't you say you'd look for another job?

05:38.000 --> 05:39.360
How did you end up doing this?

05:39.360 --> 05:40.560
And you didn't even tell me.

05:40.560 --> 05:42.760
Jobs are not that easy to find nowadays.

05:42.950 --> 05:45.240
I'm a housewife in my thirties

05:45.270 --> 05:46.659
with a blank resume.

05:47.159 --> 05:48.390
Nobody wants me anywhere.

05:48.390 --> 05:50.790
But you shouldn't have to
work as a cleaner.

05:51.800 --> 05:52.800
Tell me the truth,

05:53.070 --> 05:54.680
are you in some kind of trouble?

05:54.680 --> 05:55.600
No.

05:56.050 --> 05:56.870
Nobody forced me.

05:56.870 --> 05:58.000
I chose it myself.

05:58.560 --> 06:00.270
I haven't worked for so many years,

06:00.270 --> 06:02.240
I have to start from the bottom.

06:02.680 --> 06:03.720
Don't worry, Qiaoqi.

06:03.720 --> 06:04.390
I'm fine.

06:04.390 --> 06:06.240
I told you I'm your ladder.

06:06.270 --> 06:07.120
I've got your back.

06:07.120 --> 06:08.800
Okay, you've got my back.

06:08.800 --> 06:09.930
I'll remember that.

06:10.120 --> 06:11.040
Go back to work.

06:11.040 --> 06:12.240
I need to get busy too.

06:12.390 --> 06:13.720
Let's talk later.

06:25.480 --> 06:27.040
Sister, you scared me to death.

06:27.040 --> 06:28.100
What are you doing?

06:31.720 --> 06:33.040
Did you recruit Xu Miyu

06:33.060 --> 06:34.990
to the executive floor?

06:36.159 --> 06:36.560
Who?

06:36.800 --> 06:38.159
Xu Miyu!

06:38.800 --> 06:39.720
Xu Mi...

06:42.720 --> 06:45.480
Didn't you ask me for a favor
during the interview?

06:45.480 --> 06:47.000
Her resume didn't pass.

06:47.360 --> 06:48.560
But seeing her like that,

06:48.560 --> 06:50.710
I gave her a suggestion.

06:50.800 --> 06:51.620
So I asked her

06:51.830 --> 06:54.360
if she wanted to try
starting as an attendant.

06:56.000 --> 06:57.060
She actually came.

06:57.600 --> 06:58.240
No,

06:58.720 --> 06:59.800
I asked you to help her

06:59.800 --> 07:01.800
apply for the Marketing Department,

07:01.800 --> 07:03.720
and you sent her to be an attendant.

07:03.720 --> 07:04.360
Bro,

07:04.720 --> 07:06.040
I treat you like a brother,

07:06.040 --> 07:07.570
and you treat me like a fool?

07:07.600 --> 07:08.240
Sis,

07:08.720 --> 07:09.720
I swear to God,

07:09.720 --> 07:11.390
I wouldn't dare treat you like a fool.

07:11.390 --> 07:12.920
She seemed very anxious,

07:13.160 --> 07:15.600
and she couldn't get into
the Marketing Department anytime soon,

07:15.600 --> 07:17.130
so I thought of a way for her.

07:18.920 --> 07:20.720
Do you think she ran into some trouble

07:20.720 --> 07:22.180
and needs money urgently?

07:22.360 --> 07:23.820
Did she tell you anything?

07:36.600 --> 07:39.040
Hello. What are the last four digits
of your phone number?

07:39.040 --> 07:40.300
What last four digits?

07:40.390 --> 07:41.270
6453.

07:44.600 --> 07:46.360
What kind of secret code is this?

07:46.360 --> 07:47.120
Sir,

07:47.720 --> 07:48.720
please don't be angry.

07:48.720 --> 07:49.600
It's not a secret code.

07:49.600 --> 07:50.920
It's a ride-hailing app.

07:50.920 --> 07:51.800
Ride-hailing?

07:52.720 --> 07:53.480
Uber?

07:53.800 --> 07:54.159
Yes.

07:54.390 --> 07:55.590
It's similar to Uber.

07:55.600 --> 07:57.600
You just need to enter your destination

07:57.600 --> 07:58.890
in the address bar.

07:59.240 --> 08:00.500
It's too much trouble.

08:00.800 --> 08:02.600
In the past, you just hailed a cab

08:02.600 --> 08:03.870
and off you went.

08:04.240 --> 08:05.480
Actually, it's not that troublesome.

08:05.480 --> 08:07.010
How about I enter it for you?

08:10.240 --> 08:11.480
Excuse me, Miss...

08:11.600 --> 08:13.480
I'm from the HSKP Department
of Purong Hotel.

08:13.480 --> 08:14.480
My name is Xu Miyu.

08:15.360 --> 08:15.920
Alright.

08:16.360 --> 08:17.000
Then,

08:17.270 --> 08:18.800
thank you for your trouble.

08:20.920 --> 08:21.930
Where do you want to go?

08:21.930 --> 08:23.800
No. 18 Qinfang Garden, Aiguo Road.

08:23.800 --> 08:24.390
Okay.

08:23.920 --> 08:25.630
[Pickup: Purong Hotel]
[Destination: Qinfang Garden, Aiguo Road]

08:27.040 --> 08:27.830
Is it here?

08:28.970 --> 08:29.360
Okay.

08:29.600 --> 08:30.600
It's already entered.

08:30.600 --> 08:31.360
Please wait a moment.

08:31.360 --> 08:32.610
The car will be here shortly.

08:32.610 --> 08:33.470
That's it?

08:37.030 --> 08:38.289
This should be the car.

08:38.720 --> 08:39.840
This is great.

08:41.030 --> 08:42.080
Thank you.

08:42.150 --> 08:42.600
You're welcome,

08:42.600 --> 08:43.210
Ms. Xu.

08:43.270 --> 08:43.840
No, no.

08:44.179 --> 08:44.670
Take it.

08:44.790 --> 08:46.150
I really can't accept this.

08:46.150 --> 08:46.750
Thank you.

08:47.480 --> 08:48.280
Alright then.

08:51.030 --> 08:52.000
Thanks a lot.

08:53.710 --> 08:55.480
Goodbye.

09:01.980 --> 09:03.550
I knew I wasn't wrong about you,

09:03.550 --> 09:04.270
Xu Miyu.

09:04.790 --> 09:05.590
Director Xue.

09:06.120 --> 09:07.840
I heard you were assigned to
the executive floor.

09:07.840 --> 09:08.360
How is it?

09:08.360 --> 09:09.820
Are you used to the new job?

09:11.030 --> 09:12.360
There are many things to learn,

09:12.360 --> 09:14.030
but I'm trying my best.

09:15.030 --> 09:17.720
There's always some hardship
at the beginning.

09:18.320 --> 09:20.360
It'll be fine once you get through it.

09:20.360 --> 09:22.240
You are a person
with professional aspirations.

09:22.240 --> 09:22.900
Believe me,

09:23.120 --> 09:24.600
you'll get better and better,

09:24.600 --> 09:25.790
and go to the next level.

09:25.790 --> 09:26.390
Thank you.

09:27.150 --> 09:27.750
Keep it up.

09:36.120 --> 09:37.080
Room service.

09:39.150 --> 09:40.310
Hello, Mr. Ji.

09:40.360 --> 09:42.090
Your clothes have been washed.

09:42.790 --> 09:43.420
Thank you.

09:45.090 --> 09:46.550
Don't you want to check

09:46.600 --> 09:48.550
if it is clean

09:48.600 --> 09:50.030
or if there is any damage?

09:52.000 --> 09:53.390
It's fine. Thank you

09:53.390 --> 09:54.790
for coming all the way here.

09:54.790 --> 09:55.590
Wait a minute.

09:58.120 --> 10:00.830
Do you remember the

10:01.000 --> 10:03.460
good review thing
we talked about last time?

10:03.910 --> 10:04.600
Yes.

10:05.720 --> 10:08.390
So would this meet

10:09.120 --> 10:11.670
your standards for a good review?

10:12.240 --> 10:13.240
Do you ask guests for a good review

10:13.240 --> 10:14.480
every day at work?

10:14.770 --> 10:15.320
No.

10:15.960 --> 10:17.440
I haven't asked anyone else.

10:17.440 --> 10:19.490
So I am especially honored?

10:20.000 --> 10:21.360
Why do you want my good review?

10:21.360 --> 10:22.220
Because you...

10:24.240 --> 10:26.840
Because you are
our esteemed Black Card VIP.

10:26.840 --> 10:27.840
So?

10:30.720 --> 10:32.360
I have cleaned the room
exactly as you asked,

10:32.360 --> 10:34.120
quickly and well,

10:34.360 --> 10:36.120
and I didn't disturb you, did I?

10:36.360 --> 10:38.440
I've already received
two bad reviews this month.

10:38.440 --> 10:40.000
If I get one more,

10:40.000 --> 10:41.840
my entire bonus
for the month will be gone.

10:41.840 --> 10:45.000
-So I…
-So a good review can cancel a bad review

10:45.000 --> 10:46.020
and "buys you another life"?

10:46.020 --> 10:47.360
Who taught you this?

10:47.600 --> 10:49.360
Is it an unspoken rule
on the executive floor?

10:49.360 --> 10:49.960
Yes...

10:51.360 --> 10:53.200
I figured it out myself.

10:55.630 --> 10:57.000
As a newcomer to the workplace,

10:57.000 --> 10:59.000
instead of improving
your professional skills,

10:59.000 --> 11:01.000
you spend all day thinking about this?

11:01.000 --> 11:03.130
What does your bonus have to do with me?

11:04.320 --> 11:05.960
How can you speak like that?

11:05.960 --> 11:06.870
Am I wrong?

11:07.750 --> 11:08.480
No,

11:08.720 --> 11:09.720
you're not wrong.

11:10.000 --> 11:10.840
I'm wrong.

11:11.200 --> 11:12.240
I am unprofessional.

11:12.240 --> 11:13.750
My mistake was overestimating your

11:13.750 --> 11:15.360
pitifully small amount of empathy.

11:15.360 --> 11:16.360
Sorry.

11:16.860 --> 11:17.440
Wait.

11:19.000 --> 11:19.860
Let me tell you,

11:20.120 --> 11:21.240
if you want a good review,

11:21.240 --> 11:22.360
you first have to

11:22.360 --> 11:24.890
make the guests
genuinely like your service.

11:24.960 --> 11:26.650
Making guests feel at home.

11:30.240 --> 11:31.770
I don't need you to teach me.

11:35.360 --> 11:36.600
Makes sense, though.

11:38.300 --> 11:38.840
Mr. Ray.

11:38.840 --> 11:40.040
Sorry to startle you.

11:40.200 --> 11:41.240
I heard your voice

11:41.240 --> 11:42.360
and worried you were in trouble.

11:42.360 --> 11:42.840
Are you okay?

11:42.840 --> 11:44.180
I'm fine.

11:44.200 --> 11:44.600
No.

11:45.630 --> 11:46.720
If you don't need anything else,

11:46.720 --> 11:47.720
I'll be going now.

11:57.360 --> 11:59.690
Actually, if you need a good review,

11:59.720 --> 12:00.840
you can come to me.

12:01.200 --> 12:02.600
I'm very satisfied with you.

12:02.600 --> 12:04.840
You smell really nice today.

12:04.840 --> 12:06.240
Is it perfume?

12:06.240 --> 12:09.480
I think you would look beautiful
in this dress.

12:10.730 --> 12:13.840
[I think you would look beautiful
in this dress.]

12:18.420 --> 12:22.710
[Please don't send such messages again.]

12:26.260 --> 12:27.250
[Please don't send such messages again.]

12:27.270 --> 12:28.070
[I think you would look beautiful
in this dress.]

12:38.510 --> 12:39.190
Ms. Zhang,

12:41.600 --> 12:42.240
could you let someone else

12:42.240 --> 12:42.970
serve Mr. Ray

12:43.120 --> 12:44.960
from now on?

12:45.080 --> 12:45.840
Why?

12:46.200 --> 12:48.260
Didn't he specifically request you?

12:50.870 --> 12:52.360
He is a bit strange,

12:52.360 --> 12:55.390
always saying inappropriate things to me.

12:56.600 --> 12:57.240
Miyu,

12:57.600 --> 12:59.200
are you being too sensitive?

12:59.360 --> 13:00.960
Mr. Ray is a foreigner;

13:01.120 --> 13:03.250
there might be cultural differences.

13:03.720 --> 13:06.120
But he really makes me uncomfortable.

13:07.000 --> 13:08.320
No.

13:10.120 --> 13:11.240
Well,

13:11.440 --> 13:12.750
then just let him talk.

13:12.750 --> 13:14.240
It's not like you're losing anything.

13:14.240 --> 13:16.120
What can he do to an attendant anyway?

13:16.120 --> 13:16.600
But...

13:16.600 --> 13:17.720
Don't just stand here.

13:17.720 --> 13:19.440
You already have two bad reviews.

13:19.440 --> 13:22.040
And you still want to
be picky about customers?

13:53.440 --> 13:54.240
Good evening.

14:24.200 --> 14:26.460
Sir, let me scan the room key card
for you.

14:31.080 --> 14:31.940
Please come in.

14:36.080 --> 14:36.880
Just a moment.

14:38.720 --> 14:39.720
Your photo.

14:44.610 --> 14:46.260
Do you need any more help?

14:47.960 --> 14:49.840
I need some quiet.

15:06.320 --> 15:08.000
The last ten orders for this item today.

15:08.000 --> 15:09.960
Come on, get ready for the link.

15:09.960 --> 15:12.870
Three, two, one, link is live!

15:14.000 --> 15:14.510
Miyu,

15:15.330 --> 15:17.450
there's a promotion
in Dianjiangchun's live stream today.

15:17.450 --> 15:18.250
Did you buy it?

15:18.870 --> 15:19.630
No.

15:19.720 --> 15:21.750
By the way, an old man checked into 1810.

15:21.750 --> 15:23.680
He looks like he is in his eighties.

15:23.720 --> 15:25.120
He doesn't have any family with him.

15:25.120 --> 15:27.120
We need to pay more attention to him.

15:27.200 --> 15:27.840
Don't.

15:28.000 --> 15:29.510
That old man is very independent.

15:29.510 --> 15:30.720
He came back from abroad.

15:30.720 --> 15:32.700
I think his surname is Tan.

15:32.870 --> 15:33.270
Right.

15:33.600 --> 15:34.380
Mr. Tan.

15:34.420 --> 15:35.240
I'm telling you.

15:35.240 --> 15:36.480
That Mr. Tan

15:36.480 --> 15:38.600
is different from
the old folks here in China.

15:38.600 --> 15:40.120
If you reach out to help him up,

15:40.120 --> 15:41.240
he would be very unhappy.

15:41.240 --> 15:41.960
Anyway,

15:41.960 --> 15:42.750
at his age,

15:42.750 --> 15:44.750
it's not wrong for us
to pay more attention to him.

15:44.750 --> 15:45.870
The old man is fine.

15:46.620 --> 15:47.350
I think

15:47.750 --> 15:49.080
he is in good health.

15:49.080 --> 15:50.880
We don't need to worry about him.

15:52.360 --> 15:54.870
I don't think he's in a good state today.

15:54.870 --> 15:57.360
He looks like he has suffered
some kind of blow.

15:57.360 --> 15:58.350
You are on duty today.

15:58.350 --> 15:59.350
Keep an eye on him.

16:00.240 --> 16:01.240
I missed it again.

16:02.120 --> 16:02.920
Yin Xiang.

16:03.480 --> 16:04.360
I know.

16:04.750 --> 16:06.360
The next order is coming right up.

16:06.360 --> 16:08.220
I'll go find a place with a signal.

16:43.080 --> 16:44.540
It is completely cold now.

16:46.320 --> 16:47.320
Room service.

16:49.120 --> 16:50.630
Mr. Tan, open the door.

16:54.120 --> 16:55.000
Mr. Tan.

16:56.600 --> 16:57.510
Mr. Tan!

17:00.480 --> 17:01.320
Mr. Tan!

17:04.480 --> 17:05.480
Mr. Tan!

17:05.720 --> 17:06.119
Tan...

17:07.829 --> 17:08.440
Mr. Tan!

17:12.099 --> 17:13.060
Is anyone there?

17:13.640 --> 17:14.569
Is anyone there?

17:15.880 --> 17:16.810
Is anyone there?

17:16.960 --> 17:17.750
Help!

17:19.000 --> 17:19.930
Is anyone there?

17:20.440 --> 17:21.440
Help!

17:26.540 --> 17:27.670
[Zhang Cailu]

17:30.590 --> 17:31.880
The number you dialed...

17:31.880 --> 17:32.890
Mr. Tan!

17:33.350 --> 17:34.810
Please try it again later.

17:35.590 --> 17:36.590
Front office!

17:36.640 --> 17:38.110
The guest in 1810 has fainted.

17:38.110 --> 17:38.830
I need help.

17:38.830 --> 17:40.590
Roger that. Administer first aid.

17:40.590 --> 17:41.830
The front office will send someone
up right away.

17:41.830 --> 17:42.350
Okay.

17:43.480 --> 17:44.250
First aid.

17:46.000 --> 17:46.600
First aid.

17:54.300 --> 17:55.000
There's no one on the executive floor.

17:55.000 --> 17:56.720
You're the only one I can turn to.

17:56.720 --> 17:57.440
What is it now?

17:57.440 --> 17:58.640
The guest in 1810 fainted.

17:58.640 --> 17:59.510
He needs first aid!

17:59.510 --> 18:00.700
Can you help me?

18:01.590 --> 18:02.120
Let's go.

18:05.240 --> 18:05.720
Which way?

18:05.720 --> 18:06.380
Right side.

18:06.830 --> 18:08.240
He was lying on the floor when I came in.

18:08.240 --> 18:09.440
I've called 120.

18:09.440 --> 18:11.000
I also notified the front office.

18:11.000 --> 18:11.730
Understood.

18:12.000 --> 18:13.480
Sir! Sir!

18:13.880 --> 18:15.610
Can you hear me? Can you hear me?

18:16.880 --> 18:17.830
Lay him flat first.

18:17.830 --> 18:18.400
Okay.

18:18.400 --> 18:18.960
Here.

18:27.240 --> 18:29.030
1001, 1002, 1003,

18:29.030 --> 18:31.030
1004, 1005, 1006,

18:31.030 --> 18:32.570
1007. No pulse.

18:32.590 --> 18:33.510
I need to do CPR.

18:33.510 --> 18:34.240
Step back a bit.

18:34.240 --> 18:34.640
Give me some space.

18:34.640 --> 18:35.240
Okay.

18:54.860 --> 18:55.660
Mr. Tan!

18:55.690 --> 18:56.270
Sir!

18:56.290 --> 18:57.310
Mr. Tan, how are you?

18:57.310 --> 18:58.000
Can you hear me?

18:58.000 --> 18:59.260
The oxygen bag is here!

18:59.330 --> 19:00.590
The oxygen bag is here.

19:01.160 --> 19:02.160
Careful, slowly.

19:02.920 --> 19:03.450
This way!

19:07.070 --> 19:07.890
Help me.

19:08.240 --> 19:08.640
Okay.

19:09.790 --> 19:10.450
Help him up.

19:14.070 --> 19:15.200
One, two, up.

19:16.680 --> 19:17.200
Here.

19:17.310 --> 19:17.970
Let me do it.

19:23.810 --> 19:24.530
Let me do it.

19:25.330 --> 19:25.960
Leave it to me.

19:25.960 --> 19:26.640
Okay.

19:28.790 --> 19:29.480
Okay.

19:33.260 --> 19:34.240
Careful.

19:35.030 --> 19:36.030
What should we do?

19:38.240 --> 19:40.500
Bear with it; ambulance is almost there.

19:40.920 --> 19:41.880
Why hasn't the ambulance arrived yet?

19:41.880 --> 19:42.720
There's roadwork ahead.

19:42.720 --> 19:44.920
They're stuck two intersections west.

19:45.720 --> 19:47.250
Does anyone else have a car?

19:48.920 --> 19:49.920
Take my car!

19:50.480 --> 19:51.000
Okay.

19:52.750 --> 19:53.960
Come give me a hand.

19:57.090 --> 19:57.940
Be careful.

20:00.000 --> 20:01.440
Hello, I'm a guest here.

20:01.440 --> 20:02.520
Room 1812.

20:02.680 --> 20:03.730
If you trust me,

20:03.590 --> 20:04.510
[Purong Hotel]

20:03.920 --> 20:04.720
let me drive.

20:06.240 --> 20:07.550
Thank you so much, Mr. Ji.

20:07.550 --> 20:08.200
Okay.

20:08.640 --> 20:09.360
Sorry for the trouble.

20:09.360 --> 20:10.480
Sorry for the trouble.

20:10.480 --> 20:10.960
Sister!

20:11.000 --> 20:11.640
Sister!

20:11.750 --> 20:12.880
What happened to the guest?

20:12.880 --> 20:13.550
How is the guest?

20:13.550 --> 20:15.270
We're taking him to the hospital now.

20:15.270 --> 20:16.230
Hurry back to your shift.

20:16.230 --> 20:17.030
Wait, Sister.

20:17.070 --> 20:18.590
I really didn't hear it just now.

20:18.590 --> 20:19.260
I really...

20:19.310 --> 20:19.640
I...

20:19.640 --> 20:22.040
-Watch your hands.
-I wanted to check on him

20:22.480 --> 20:25.080
as soon as I finished
watching the live stream.

20:26.370 --> 20:29.220
[Emergency]

20:29.250 --> 20:34.070
[Emergency Room]

20:31.480 --> 20:32.240
Hello, Ms. An.

20:32.240 --> 20:35.000
I'm Xu Miyu, an attendant
from the executive floor.

20:35.000 --> 20:36.400
I've taken the guest to the hospital.

20:36.400 --> 20:37.780
He's in emergency care now.

20:37.780 --> 20:40.300
I don't know the exact situation yet.

20:39.280 --> 20:42.760
[Emergency Room]

20:40.480 --> 20:42.430
Do you need me
to send someone to help you?

20:42.430 --> 20:44.070
No need. You don't have to send anyone.

20:44.070 --> 20:45.240
I'm off work anyway.

20:45.240 --> 20:46.970
I can keep an eye on things here.

20:47.000 --> 20:47.850
Yin Xiang.

20:48.030 --> 20:50.190
Remember to clean room 1810.

20:50.520 --> 20:52.440
I've taken the guest to the hospital.

20:52.440 --> 20:53.690
He's in emergency care now.

20:52.520 --> 20:56.010
[Emergency Room]

20:53.880 --> 20:55.030
If Ms. Zhang asks,

20:55.050 --> 20:56.650
tell her to contact Ms. Anna.

20:56.680 --> 20:57.640
Okay. Thank you.

21:11.510 --> 21:12.310
Mr. Ji,

21:13.000 --> 21:14.360
thank you for today.

21:17.000 --> 21:19.660
Didn't you say
I have pitifully little empathy?

21:21.240 --> 21:23.710
I'm sorry. I shouldn't have said that.

21:23.790 --> 21:25.440
But you...

21:25.460 --> 21:26.020
But what?

21:27.200 --> 21:28.730
You were really helpful.

21:28.920 --> 21:30.660
Thanks to you today.

21:30.920 --> 21:32.240
Thank you so much

21:32.240 --> 21:33.460
for helping us.

21:36.880 --> 21:37.680
It's nothing.

21:38.030 --> 21:40.790
In the face of life and death, there's no
such thing as being willing or unwilling.

21:40.790 --> 21:41.920
I'm honored

21:43.070 --> 21:44.330
that you thought of me.

21:47.410 --> 21:48.310
It's getting late.

21:48.310 --> 21:49.680
You should go back and rest early.

21:49.680 --> 21:51.410
I'll keep an eye on things here.

21:53.270 --> 21:54.270
Family of Tan Jiaming.

21:54.270 --> 21:55.160
Here!

21:57.480 --> 21:58.750
It's acute myocardial infarction.

21:57.640 --> 22:00.660
[Emergency Room]

21:59.240 --> 22:00.750
Fortunately, you performed CPR

22:00.750 --> 22:02.200
and brought him in in time.

22:02.200 --> 22:03.000
Our interventional surgery

22:03.000 --> 22:03.860
went smoothly.

22:03.890 --> 22:04.480
Now the patient

22:04.480 --> 22:06.140
is temporarily out of danger.

22:07.400 --> 22:08.080
Great.

22:09.160 --> 22:10.920
When can the patient be discharged?

22:10.920 --> 22:12.400
The patient is quite old,

22:12.400 --> 22:14.070
so he needs to stay in the hospital
for a few more days of observation.

22:14.070 --> 22:14.880
I understand, doctor.

22:14.880 --> 22:15.480
Thank you.

22:27.230 --> 22:29.390
[Emergency Room]

22:46.640 --> 22:47.640
You didn't leave?

22:50.720 --> 22:51.320
Thank you.

22:52.920 --> 22:55.850
How many times are you going to say
thank you tonight?

22:56.510 --> 22:58.000
Only one person needs to stay.

22:58.000 --> 23:00.330
The ward is small.
Don't all crowd in here.

23:01.030 --> 23:02.030
You go back first.

23:07.030 --> 23:08.890
Ms. An's car needs to be returned.

23:08.920 --> 23:10.650
I can keep an eye on things here.

23:12.790 --> 23:13.270
Then...

23:14.550 --> 23:15.440
Remember to eat.

23:15.440 --> 23:16.230
Thank you.

23:47.510 --> 23:49.510
Thank you for your hard work, Mr. Ji.

23:49.550 --> 23:50.350
It's nothing.

23:50.750 --> 23:52.160
Thank you for your selfless help.

23:52.160 --> 23:54.070
Here, I'll give you the keys first.

23:54.070 --> 23:55.000
Well...

23:55.000 --> 23:57.060
Has the patient's family been found?

23:57.480 --> 23:58.880
We're already looking.

23:59.270 --> 24:00.270
We only know that

24:00.270 --> 24:02.350
the patient is an ethnic Chinese
from the US.

24:02.350 --> 24:04.400
He used a US passport when registering.

24:04.400 --> 24:06.130
Other information is unknown.

24:06.160 --> 24:08.240
We're already contacting the embassy.

24:08.240 --> 24:08.920
Okay.

24:08.920 --> 24:10.780
Let me know if there's any update.

24:10.790 --> 24:11.440
What?

24:13.720 --> 24:14.520
Nothing. I...

24:14.790 --> 24:17.250
I just want to know
the patient's condition.

24:18.480 --> 24:19.000
Okay.

24:20.440 --> 24:21.550
Rest early.

24:21.550 --> 24:22.400
Okay.

24:27.250 --> 24:29.390
[Outpatient Building]

24:38.750 --> 24:39.480
Nurse,

24:40.070 --> 24:41.640
how is the patient doing?

24:42.240 --> 24:43.440
He's basically stable.

24:43.440 --> 24:45.640
We'll give him IV fluids for two more days
to stabilize his condition.

24:45.640 --> 24:46.960
Okay, thank you.

24:52.510 --> 24:55.000
Mr. Tan, you're awake.

24:56.750 --> 24:58.410
The sun is already out.

25:00.070 --> 25:01.160
I'm well-rested.

25:01.160 --> 25:02.680
Time to get up.

25:03.950 --> 25:05.280
You can't get out of bed.

25:05.790 --> 25:07.050
We are in the hospital.

25:07.400 --> 25:07.880
In...

25:08.440 --> 25:09.410
In the hospital?

25:09.880 --> 25:10.880
How did I get here?

25:11.440 --> 25:12.960
Who brought me here?

25:14.310 --> 25:16.120
No wonder I kept

25:16.510 --> 25:17.980
having nightmares last night.

25:17.980 --> 25:18.870
I want to go out.

25:19.160 --> 25:20.290
Where are you going?

25:23.400 --> 25:24.620
Hello.

25:24.680 --> 25:26.880
Are you Mr. Tan's family?

25:27.240 --> 25:28.430
I'm his friend.

25:29.070 --> 25:30.070
Who are you?

25:30.270 --> 25:31.270
I'm Xu Miyu,

25:31.270 --> 25:32.750
an attendant from the HSKP Department
at Purong Hotel.

25:32.750 --> 25:34.200
Xu Miyu?

25:35.720 --> 25:36.920
This stubborn old man

25:37.160 --> 25:38.490
must have troubled you.

25:39.000 --> 25:40.260
Not at all. It's my job.

25:41.480 --> 25:42.880
Is Tan Jiaming's family here?

25:42.880 --> 25:44.510
Please go through the
admission procedures.

25:44.510 --> 25:45.160
I'll go.

25:45.880 --> 25:46.400
Here.

25:47.270 --> 25:48.480
Take this bank card.

25:49.680 --> 25:51.400
The PIN is 330915.

25:51.400 --> 25:52.330
Okay, thank you.

25:57.270 --> 25:58.720
You even know how to hide it, huh?

25:58.720 --> 25:59.960
If Jizhou hadn't

26:00.200 --> 26:01.880
called me early this morning,

26:02.160 --> 26:03.440
I wouldn't have come to the hospital

26:03.440 --> 26:05.000
and wasted my time with you.

26:05.680 --> 26:07.300
You had a heart attack!

26:07.640 --> 26:09.570
Don't you know how serious that is?

26:10.160 --> 26:11.030
It's an old problem.

26:11.030 --> 26:12.400
Doctors just like to scare people.

26:12.400 --> 26:14.060
They make it sound so serious.

26:14.550 --> 26:15.480
Ms. An,

26:15.790 --> 26:17.280
the guest in 1810

26:17.310 --> 26:19.040
needs to be hospitalized
for observation for a few days.

26:19.040 --> 26:20.320
His family has arrived.

26:19.260 --> 26:22.960
[Nurse Station]

26:20.380 --> 26:22.000
Okay, come back first.

26:22.450 --> 26:23.980
I've already told Ms. Zhang

26:24.000 --> 26:26.000
about your performance last night.

26:26.030 --> 26:26.790
Thank you, Ms. An.

26:26.790 --> 26:28.000
It's all part of my job.

26:28.000 --> 26:28.720
Thank you.

26:29.160 --> 26:29.720
Okay.

26:31.690 --> 26:33.080
I'm sorry, Ms. An.

26:33.310 --> 26:34.790
I was on shift rotation yesterday

26:34.790 --> 26:35.920
and was with my kid for an exam.

26:35.920 --> 26:37.030
My phone was off.

26:37.240 --> 26:38.500
Sorry for the trouble.

26:38.680 --> 26:39.680
It was no trouble.

26:39.920 --> 26:41.030
I'm actually happy for you.

26:41.030 --> 26:42.400
The attendant under you

26:42.400 --> 26:43.950
is so responsible

26:44.160 --> 26:45.400
and quick to react.

26:45.720 --> 26:46.720
She handled

26:46.720 --> 26:47.960
such an urgent situation

26:47.960 --> 26:49.160
perfectly in no time.

26:49.400 --> 26:51.070
The guest is out of danger now,

26:51.350 --> 26:52.680
so we are all relieved.

26:53.550 --> 26:54.240
The guest's family

26:54.240 --> 26:55.750
even called from abroad

26:55.750 --> 26:56.960
to thank our hotel.

26:57.590 --> 26:59.030
The attendants on your executive floor

26:59.030 --> 27:00.240
deserve the most praise.

27:00.240 --> 27:00.990
No problem.

27:01.200 --> 27:03.000
I'll definitely praise her
when I get back.

27:03.000 --> 27:04.060
Excuse me, cousin.

27:04.400 --> 27:05.750
Go help me get something.

27:05.750 --> 27:07.210
It's in the jacket pocket.

27:11.790 --> 27:12.390
Is it this?

27:16.200 --> 27:17.030
Look.

27:18.030 --> 27:18.720
Ahui

27:19.720 --> 27:20.810
is already gone.

27:21.750 --> 27:23.810
I went to his house yesterday morning

27:23.880 --> 27:25.080
and happened to catch

27:26.000 --> 27:27.920
the seventh day of his passing.

27:28.680 --> 27:30.550
The one in the middle is Liang.

27:31.070 --> 27:32.720
When I went to see him,

27:33.070 --> 27:35.400
he just stared at me blankly,

27:35.960 --> 27:37.240
shedding tears,

27:37.550 --> 27:39.110
unable to say a word.

27:40.510 --> 27:42.310
He has been paralyzed for a year.

27:43.240 --> 27:44.030
In the end,

27:44.480 --> 27:45.160
Ming

27:45.720 --> 27:48.650
was taken to Shenzhen
by his daughter to settle down.

27:49.200 --> 27:51.240
I am the only one left.

27:55.270 --> 27:56.680
Decades have passed.

27:59.680 --> 28:00.720
It went too fast.

28:02.230 --> 28:06.240
[Gao Hong-19th Floor-Rest shift]
[Luo Qingping-18th Floor-Day shift ]

28:06.260 --> 28:11.790
[Yin Xiang-18th Floor-Day shift
-Positive feedback]

28:12.030 --> 28:12.790
Last night,

28:13.030 --> 28:15.760
the guest in 1810
suffered a sudden heart attack.

28:15.790 --> 28:17.250
Yin Xiang, who was on duty,

28:17.270 --> 28:19.240
immediately reported to
the relevant hotel departments

28:19.240 --> 28:21.240
and rushed the patient
to the hospital in time.

28:21.240 --> 28:22.640
She is hereby commended.

28:23.270 --> 28:24.310
Not bad, little Xiang.

28:24.310 --> 28:25.960
Why didn't you mention such a big thing?

28:25.960 --> 28:28.160
Treat us to a meal when you get the bonus.

28:29.750 --> 28:30.310
Miyu,

28:30.960 --> 28:32.090
don't be late again.

28:32.920 --> 28:33.510
Got it.

28:35.200 --> 28:36.890
Everyone, cheer up.

28:37.000 --> 28:39.440
This month is
the service quality supervision month.

28:39.440 --> 28:41.570
Don't slack off or be late.

28:41.750 --> 28:44.030
If you ruin the reputation
of the HSKP Department,

28:44.030 --> 28:45.750
I can't protect you in front of Mr. Feng.

28:45.750 --> 28:46.480
Understood?

28:46.480 --> 28:47.620
Understood.

28:47.750 --> 28:48.550
Get to work.

29:10.550 --> 29:11.400
Miyu.

29:17.400 --> 29:18.110
Yin Xiang.

29:20.000 --> 29:22.000
Don't you have anything to say to me?

29:22.030 --> 29:22.550
I...

29:24.400 --> 29:25.170
Miyu.

29:26.030 --> 29:28.070
I didn't mean to steal your credit.

29:28.790 --> 29:31.240
A life-threatening incident
happened last night.

29:31.240 --> 29:33.500
I was afraid that if the management knew,

29:34.000 --> 29:35.860
I would lose my salary this month.

29:38.240 --> 29:39.360
Don't be mad.

29:40.550 --> 29:42.210
Please don't expose me, okay?

29:44.290 --> 29:45.300
You have it hard.

29:46.030 --> 29:47.090
We all have it hard.

29:48.510 --> 29:50.510
We both work on the executive floor.

29:50.550 --> 29:52.880
We inevitably need to help each other out,

29:53.440 --> 29:54.480
right?

29:55.440 --> 29:56.570
I understand, Miyu.

29:56.720 --> 29:57.780
I owe you this time.

29:58.000 --> 29:59.000
Next time you need me,

29:59.000 --> 30:00.530
I will definitely help you.

30:22.750 --> 30:23.480
Take a break.

30:24.980 --> 30:25.580
Thank you.

30:32.880 --> 30:34.610
You are an interesting person.

30:35.440 --> 30:36.970
When a bad review
that shouldn't fall on you

30:36.970 --> 30:38.830
was pinned on you, you endured it.

30:39.590 --> 30:41.160
When the good review
that rightfully belonged to you

30:41.160 --> 30:42.160
went to someone else,

30:42.160 --> 30:43.360
you still endured it.

30:43.510 --> 30:44.510
Are you

30:45.030 --> 30:46.200
a people pleaser?

30:54.200 --> 30:55.240
I am not trying to please anyone.

30:55.240 --> 30:58.640
I just think everyone
has their own difficulties,

30:58.750 --> 31:01.350
and I don't want to
make things hard for others.

31:15.270 --> 31:16.000
What is it now?

31:16.000 --> 31:17.240
I want to ask you a favor.

31:17.240 --> 31:18.280
Ask me?

31:18.510 --> 31:20.270
Could you go to any room

31:20.790 --> 31:22.030
on the executive floor

31:22.030 --> 31:24.150
and get me a bottle of shampoo,

31:24.960 --> 31:26.720
then go to the storage room

31:26.720 --> 31:28.030
and take a new one—

31:28.750 --> 31:30.440
one that has just been
logged into inventory?

31:30.440 --> 31:30.880
Why...

31:30.880 --> 31:31.810
Don't ask me why.

31:32.430 --> 31:34.030
Just tell me if you can or not.

31:36.290 --> 31:37.030
Sure.

31:38.720 --> 31:40.180
But you can't tell anyone.

31:40.480 --> 31:41.880
Because I only trust you.

32:10.640 --> 32:13.070
[Shower Gel]

32:17.910 --> 32:19.210
[Shampoo]

32:27.510 --> 32:28.270
Miyu.

32:28.440 --> 32:29.070
Ms. Zhang.

32:38.080 --> 32:42.240
[1817 Empty]

32:57.750 --> 32:59.270
[Conditioner] [Shower Gel]

33:08.640 --> 33:09.650
Room service.

33:11.920 --> 33:12.850
Come in.

33:24.480 --> 33:25.280
Did you get it?

33:27.340 --> 33:31.080
[Shampoo] [Storage]

33:30.680 --> 33:31.280
Remember,

33:31.680 --> 33:32.960
keep today's matter a secret.

33:32.960 --> 33:35.020
You absolutely must not tell anyone.

33:36.400 --> 33:37.660
Then I have a question.

33:38.070 --> 33:39.450
Can you guarantee

33:39.790 --> 33:40.480
that this

33:40.480 --> 33:42.790
won't affect the hotel's
normal service operations?

33:42.790 --> 33:44.680
Are you bargaining with a guest?

33:45.960 --> 33:46.960
It's my duty.

33:49.440 --> 33:49.920
Okay.

33:50.240 --> 33:50.970
Don't worry.

34:08.320 --> 34:09.920
Can we pause tomorrow's shipment

34:09.920 --> 34:11.480
for a bit before sending it out?

34:11.480 --> 34:13.960
The prepaid payment has already
gone into your pocket.

34:13.960 --> 34:15.510
How can you cut off the supply?

34:15.510 --> 34:16.710
The goods aren't ready?

34:16.710 --> 34:18.150
It's not about the goods.

34:18.550 --> 34:19.760
I'm worried

34:19.760 --> 34:21.230
that doing this is too risky.

34:21.230 --> 34:22.690
What if someone finds out?

34:23.400 --> 34:25.320
Who could possibly find out?

34:25.760 --> 34:28.420
There's an attendant
on our floor named Xu Miyu.

34:28.510 --> 34:29.670
Xu Miyu?

34:30.630 --> 34:31.230
Who is she?

34:32.070 --> 34:32.880
A newbie.

34:34.719 --> 34:35.590
A rookie,

34:35.590 --> 34:36.510
and you can't handle her?

34:36.510 --> 34:37.320
No.

34:37.710 --> 34:38.630
I saw...

34:39.480 --> 34:40.760
I saw her take a bottle of shampoo

34:40.760 --> 34:43.260
from a guest room in a baffling way.

34:43.400 --> 34:44.760
I don't know what she's doing.

34:44.760 --> 34:46.090
And I didn't dare to ask.

34:46.190 --> 34:47.000
I'm worried

34:47.320 --> 34:49.280
she might have found out something.

34:49.280 --> 34:50.010
Zhang Cailu,

34:50.230 --> 34:51.090
let me tell you,

34:51.150 --> 34:52.860
get things straightened out.

34:53.070 --> 34:53.710
Are you the forewoman,

34:53.710 --> 34:54.400
or is she?

34:54.710 --> 34:56.400
You can't manage

34:56.400 --> 34:57.330
a new attendant?

34:57.510 --> 34:58.510
Do you still want to take your daughter

34:58.510 --> 34:59.960
to the Maldives for New Year's Eve?

34:59.960 --> 35:01.580
Yes, of course I do.

35:01.960 --> 35:05.000
But I'm on edge every day.

35:06.070 --> 35:07.630
The pressure is overwhelming.

35:07.630 --> 35:09.000
My body can't take it.

35:10.510 --> 35:12.000
Why didn't you say that

35:12.000 --> 35:13.330
when you took the money?

35:13.480 --> 35:14.550
You just want to make money

35:14.550 --> 35:15.880
without taking responsibility.

35:15.880 --> 35:17.710
If your body really can't take it,
stop doing it.

35:17.710 --> 35:19.840
There are plenty of people who want to.

35:20.110 --> 35:21.150
No, no.

35:22.030 --> 35:23.360
I don't mean any of that.

35:23.400 --> 35:24.220
I mean,

35:24.510 --> 35:25.230
I definitely won't let

35:25.230 --> 35:26.560
that Xu Miyu off.

35:26.800 --> 35:28.070
In a few days, I'll find a random excuse

35:28.070 --> 35:29.110
to fire her.

35:29.590 --> 35:31.510
I definitely won't cause you any trouble.

35:31.510 --> 35:33.070
I don't care how you do it.

35:33.070 --> 35:34.590
Make it look good.

35:34.800 --> 35:35.800
Don't delay my plans!

35:35.800 --> 35:36.400
Okay.

35:36.550 --> 35:37.350
Rest assured.

36:01.070 --> 36:01.760
Miyu.

36:04.960 --> 36:05.860
Um...

36:07.510 --> 36:08.630
Are you

36:09.230 --> 36:10.290
a people-pleaser?

36:10.920 --> 36:12.510
Don't tell me you want to change shifts.

36:12.510 --> 36:13.110
I don't have time.

36:13.110 --> 36:14.640
I'm not changing shifts.

36:15.150 --> 36:15.760
I...

36:18.840 --> 36:20.440
I want to tell you something.

36:20.960 --> 36:22.070
Here you are.

36:25.360 --> 36:26.760
What are you talking about?

36:26.760 --> 36:27.760
N... Nothing.

36:28.840 --> 36:30.000
I was going to ask you something.

36:30.000 --> 36:32.460
Was your leave for tomorrow
approved or not?

36:54.710 --> 36:56.350
I don't need help.

36:56.470 --> 36:57.550
Welcome to Purong Hotel.

36:57.550 --> 36:58.190
After you, Princess.

36:58.190 --> 36:58.710
Please.

37:11.630 --> 37:12.480
Welcome back.

37:12.480 --> 37:13.190
Mr. Tan.

37:13.510 --> 37:14.670
We meet again,

37:14.760 --> 37:15.550
Xu Miyu.

37:19.360 --> 37:20.590
What is this?

37:21.400 --> 37:23.800
This is a safety handrail
prepared for you.

37:24.030 --> 37:25.360
Why wouldn't I be safe?

37:25.360 --> 37:26.590
Am I that old?

37:27.150 --> 37:28.620
How old are you?

37:28.920 --> 37:30.360
Don't be ungrateful.

37:45.710 --> 37:47.770
That's very thoughtful of you, Miyu.

37:48.630 --> 37:50.000
Very thoughtful, Miyu.

37:50.150 --> 37:51.760
I can use it

37:51.760 --> 37:53.220
for exercise and fitness.

37:53.650 --> 37:54.800
Be careful.

37:55.230 --> 37:56.040
Watch out.

37:59.550 --> 38:00.510
Mr. Tan.

38:02.550 --> 38:04.360
You old rascal.

38:04.710 --> 38:06.030
I am old.

38:07.230 --> 38:07.840
Miyu,

38:07.840 --> 38:08.760
you're really thoughtful.

38:08.760 --> 38:09.590
Thank you.

38:09.590 --> 38:10.360
Come here.

38:10.480 --> 38:11.740
Take a break. Sit down.

38:30.280 --> 38:31.480
[5:00 AM, Monday, Back Kitchen Door]

38:37.540 --> 38:47.330
[Back Kitchen Area—No Unauthorized Entry]

38:50.090 --> 38:50.650
[Back Kitchen Area—No Unauthorized Entry]

38:52.210 --> 38:53.950
[Back Kitchen Area—No Unauthorized Entry]

38:57.560 --> 38:57.820
[Loading]

38:57.980 --> 38:59.450
[Deposit to someone]

39:28.630 --> 39:29.630
You startled me.

39:47.630 --> 39:49.230
Does it still taste the same?

39:51.510 --> 39:52.960
Have you really not eaten

39:52.960 --> 39:53.600
in ages?

39:55.440 --> 39:56.440
That's going too far.

39:56.440 --> 39:58.970
Are you even snatching food
from your senior?

39:59.070 --> 39:59.870
Here, senior.

40:01.070 --> 40:01.670
Boss,

40:02.150 --> 40:03.960
another steamer of soup dumplings, please.

40:03.960 --> 40:04.480
Coming.

40:06.110 --> 40:07.570
You really do love eating,

40:07.960 --> 40:10.070
or are you just pretending to
be nostalgic about home?

40:10.070 --> 40:11.800
Senior, you are like a food map.

40:11.880 --> 40:14.070
It's a pity you're in the
Finance Department.

40:14.070 --> 40:15.550
You should go to the Marketing Department

40:15.550 --> 40:16.480
or the sales department.

40:16.480 --> 40:18.140
The F&B Department works too.

40:19.030 --> 40:21.110
I'll take that as a compliment
on my versatility.

40:21.110 --> 40:22.510
As for the skills of eating,

40:22.510 --> 40:24.170
I will teach you slowly later.

40:24.550 --> 40:25.480
Whatever I ask you next,

40:25.480 --> 40:26.360
just answer it.

40:26.960 --> 40:28.620
Promise me you won't pretend.

40:28.960 --> 40:29.890
First question.

40:30.070 --> 40:32.670
Why did you go to
the kitchen's back door today?

40:34.150 --> 40:35.710
Didn't you encourage me to?

40:41.550 --> 40:42.120
Yes.

40:43.510 --> 40:44.150
I want to know

40:44.150 --> 40:45.360
what today's Purong Hotel

40:45.360 --> 40:46.680
has really become.

40:46.760 --> 40:48.820
So, what do you think after seeing it?

40:49.510 --> 40:50.840
The great tree of Purong

40:51.550 --> 40:52.590
looks glorious on the outside,

40:52.590 --> 40:53.450
but in reality,

40:53.710 --> 40:55.070
it has been hollowed out
by termites on the inside.

40:55.070 --> 40:55.550
Okay.

40:55.590 --> 40:56.590
Second question.

40:57.190 --> 40:58.450
Coming back this time,

40:58.670 --> 40:59.880
what exactly are you here for?
